data.description: Double Door Entry, 3 bedroom 2 bath with Huge Screened Patio and Garage Villa! This property features an Open kitchen with Upgraded white cabinets. Master Bedroom has a walk in closet Dual sinks. This community has two pools and a walking trail. Close to Beaches, Lawnwood Stadiums, Indian River State College, Historic Downdown and Lawnwood Hospital.  Insurance, Water and Sewer included in Monthly HOA fee
